# Jobber API - required for appointment booking
# Get your access token from: https://developer.getjobber.com/
# 1. Create a Jobber Developer Center account
# 2. Create an app with scopes: clients:write, requests:write
# 3. Connect your Jobber account via OAuth and obtain the access token
# 4. For Custom Integrations: use the token from "Test in GraphiQL"
JOBBER_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_jobber_access_token_here
